title: Folimax 5 Tablet
description: Folimax tablets contains a rich formulation of complex organic compounds known as Folic Acid (Vitamin B9). Folic Acid is an essential water soluble Vitamin for nucleotide biosynthesis and remethylation of homocysteine.
